{"tid":431252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 蔡英文向外賓介紹珍奶 介紹完忍不住喝一口!!!!!!!","createTime":"2017-10-10T13:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T14:57:29.000Z","uid":5812,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3f7a183e2b0ede689320fc64756502eed82f01b7","tid":431252,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/214927_7473c81136f6a4386d4a9fee0294b82c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F214927_7473c81136f6a4386d4a9fee0294b82c.jpg&h=e11c4e36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔡總統介紹完珍奶後，也忍不住低頭喝幾口。記者徐偉真/攝影"},{"pid":"69a0a1e2112a870384c599c975add514c9eab33b","tid":431252,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2567229264c3c46c796ecedb04314c6560d5569d","tid":431252,"uid":2054,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://jonathanwu.leng.hk/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/20120707000032M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjonathanwu.leng.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F09%2F20120707000032M.jpg&h=afb457b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0809bd4debcb11822884c275479f8322a85e040a","tid":431252,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5079f256c5ef9a1ead7350a125ada97d8c2c1915","tid":431252,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/10/10/realtime/4099239.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2Frealtime%2F4099239.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=27e8ccc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/10/10/realtime/4099244.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2Frealtime%2F4099244.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=c00a3233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國慶酒會今晚在台北賓館登場，蔡英文總統及副總統陳建仁、行政院長賴清德陪伴友邦總理逛現場台灣特色小吃攤位，蔡總統還在珍珠奶茶的攤位前化身美食大使，向宏都拉斯副總統葛芭拉介紹珍珠奶茶，推薦對方一定要喝喝看。<br />\n<br />\n外交部今晚在台北賓館舉行國慶酒會，現場有許多台灣特色小吃攤位，包括小籠包、珍珠奶茶、割包、造型棉花糖、麵線等等，約四千名外賓到場參加，場面熱鬧；今年棉花糖製作成小鴨、冰淇淋的造型，讓外賓大呼可愛，成為現場人氣最旺的攤位，攤位前排了長長人龍。<br />\n<br />\n外交部表示，本年國慶主題為「2017一起更好」，為了呼應主題，國慶酒會結合在地與國際元素、營造四海同歡的氣氛，並展現台灣豐富的生命力，酒會除提供我國各地傳統美食外，另特別準備亞洲美食、西式美食、清真美食及素食料理等，入口更有使用多種蘭花布置的花藝設計。<br />\n<br />\n陳建仁和賴清德先到場，陪同葛芭拉、吐瓦魯總理索本嘉、巴拉圭最高法院院長貝尼德斯逛美食攤位，蔡英文因為行程延遲，稍晚才抵達。<br />\n<br />\n蔡總統抵達後一行人到珍珠奶茶攤位，蔡總統向索本嘉詳細介紹珍珠奶茶，建議對方一定要品嘗，還拿托盤上的其他珍珠奶茶往後傳給身後的其他外賓；蔡總統介紹完珍珠奶茶後，店員遞給她一杯珍奶，蔡總統立刻拔開吸管開始喝，連喝了好幾口。<br />\n<br />\n蔡總統喝了幾口之後，開始和葛芭拉聊起珍珠奶茶，葛芭拉很好奇珍奶的製作方式，蔡英文向葛芭拉介紹，還告訴她珍珠是怎麼做的。<br />\n<br />\n隨後蔡總統陪同外賓到主舞台觀看台北戲曲學院的表演，也向外賓介紹表演節目，看了一下便離開，搭機前往台東觀賞煙火。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6656/2749128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F2749128&d=rClWMGmvypBpYy8zADHpIzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=c7bca7f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6656/2749128</a>"},{"pid":"48d8017086e1e9c1bc05694fe54b39fade2902fd","tid":431252,"uid":3549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"屌你啦 人地咁撚大篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6656/2749128\" data-s